search:typescript-eslint-rules:advanced.content:
- Install `@typescript-eslint/parser` and `@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin`.
- Use the latest ESLint version.
- Configure rules in `.eslintrc.json`:
  ```json
  {
    "parser": "@typescript-eslint/parser",
    "plugins": ["@typescript-eslint"],
    "rules": {
      // Add your rules here
    }
  }
  ```
- Enable Tier 2 and Tier 3 rules for better code quality.
- Example rule: `"@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any": "error"` to avoid using `any`.
- Run ESLint with the command: `eslint --ext .ts,.tsx src/`.
